snippet.title: RWW News: Even Pat Robertson Attacks Creationism As A "Joke"

localized.description:
http://www.rightwingwatch.org/content/even-pat-robertson-thinks-young-earth-creationism-joke
Right Wing Watch reports on the extreme rhetoric and activities of key right-wing figures and organizations by showing their views in their own words. In this video, Pat Robertson says he disagrees with Young Earth Creationism and considers it a "joke."
